title: SpaceX's Dragon
description: International Space Station Commander Alexander Gerst viewed SpaceX’s Dragon cargo craft chasing the orbital laboratory on Dec. 8, 2018. Gerst watched as the Dragon approached the station and took a series of photographs, saying "Hard to decide which photo of the approaching SpaceX Dragon 16 is the most stunning."
